Exterior: Field-Tested

Versatile but expensive, the German-made MP7 SMG is the perfect choice for high-impact close-range combat. It has been spray-painted freehand with short, thick lines in contrasting colors. Perfect for the insurgent on the go
The Safehouse Collection

The Negev is a beast that can keep the enemy at bay with its pin-point supressive fire, provided you have the luxury of time to gain control over it. It has been custom painted with a monstrous design and then distressed. Get back here, I'm talking to you!
The Falchion Collection
Exterior: Field-Tested
Manufactured in Switzerland, the cutting-edge MP9 SMG is an ergonomic polymer weapon favored by private security firms. It has been spray-painted using short pieces of tape as stencils.
The Dust 2 Collection
Exterior: Well-Worn
The Nova's rock-bottom price tag makes it a great ambush weapon for a cash-strapped team. It has been spray-painted in a zebra stripe pattern.
The Dust 2 Collection
Exterior: Field-Tested

The R8 Revolver delivers a highly accurate and powerful round at the expense of a lengthy trigger-pull. Firing rapidly by fanning the hammer may be the best option when point-blank stopping power is required. It has been spray-painted using a tangle of masking tape as a stencil. True power is demonstrated with subtle application
The Bank Collection
Exterior: Field-Tested
This item commemorates the 2021 PGL Stockholm CS:GO Championship.
It was dropped during the Semifinal match between Natus Vincere and Gambit Esports.

Essentially a box that bullets come out of, the MAC-10 SMG boasts a high rate of fire, with poor spread accuracy and high recoil as trade-offs. A damask flower pattern has been spray-painted atop the weapon's tan-colored base. Technically the best camouflages are the ones you don't notice...
The 2021 Mirage Collection
Sticker: PGL (Gold) | Stockholm 2021, Gambit Gaming (Gold) | Stockholm 2021, Mirage (Gold), Natus Vincere (Gold) | Stockholm 2021

Powerful and reliable, the AK-47 is one of the most popular assault rifles in the world. It is most deadly in short, controlled bursts of fire. A custom paint job of various tribal patterns has been applied. We share the same canoe
The Prisma Collection
Exterior: Factory New

The classic Sawed-Off deals very heavy close-range damage, but with its low accuracy, high spread and slow rate of fire, you'd better kill what you hit. It has been hand painted with the image of a woman with wings. Serenity is a luxury few can afford - Valeria Jenner, Revolutionary
The Chroma Collection
Exterior: Field-Tested

Highly accurate and armor-piercing, the pricy Five-Seven is a slow-loader that compensates with a generous 20-round magazine and forgiving recoil. It has been given a light blue DDPAT hydrographic as well as a custom painted slide. I don't profit from war, I profit from the human condition... - Booth, Arms Dealer
The Wildfire Collection
Exterior: Minimal Wear

The XM1014 is a powerful fully automatic shotgun that justifies its heftier price tag with the ability to paint a room with lead fast. A custom paint job has been applied with a rust-colored base and white detailing. Not to be used as a load-bearing support
The Clutch Collection
Exterior: Minimal Wear

The Bizon SMG is low-damage, but offers a uniquely designed high-capacity drum magazine that reloads quickly. It has individual parts spray-painted solid colors in a red and black color scheme. Great on cars, better on weapons
The 2018 Inferno Collection
Exterior: Minimal Wear

An ideal pistol for the Terrorist on the move, the Tec-9 is lethal in close quarters and features a high magazine capacity. It has been painted with metallic paint and uses a crystallizing mask to create a pattern. Everyone wants to make an impact
The Train Collection

This Music Kit will replace all of the music in the game and is shareable with anyone you are playing with. It also includes an MVP Anthem that plays for everyone in the match when you are MVP.

The Music Kit replaces the following music:
- Main Menu
- Round Start and End
- Map Objective
- Ten Second Warning
- Death Camera
